data.name: grdWatchList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.NUR_WRDT , A.DETAIL_GUBUN , FN_NUR_LOAD_CODE_NAME('WATCHLIST', A.DETAIL_GUBUN) , A.GWA , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(A.GWA, A.NUR_WRDT) , A.HO_DONG , A.HO_CODE , A.BUNHO , FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) , FN_OCS_LOAD_AGE(A.BUNHO, SYSDATE) , B.SEX , A.SANG , A.COMMENT1 , A.COMMENT2 , A.COMMENT3 FROM NUR5024 A , OUT0101 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND A.GUBUN = '2' -- WATCHLIST AND A.NUR_WRDT = :f_date AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong ORDER BY HO_CODE, BUNHO

data.name: grdNURCnt.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT :f_date NUR_WRDT , :f_ho_dong HO_DONG , B.CODE NUR_GRADE , B.CODE_NAME NUR_GRADE_NAME , NVL(DAWN_CNT, 0) DAWN_CNT , NVL(DAY_CNT, 0) DAY_CNT , NVL(NIGHT_CNT, 0) NIGHT_CNT , NVL(HOLI_CNT, 0) HOLI_CNT , NVL(PAY_CNT, 0) PAY_CNT , NVL(CHILDCARE_CNT, 0) CHILDCARE_CNT , NVL(SPECIAL_CNT, 0) SPECIAL_CNT , NVL(STUDY_CNT, 0) STUDY_CNT , NVL(ABSENCE_CNT, 0) ABSENCE_CNT FROM NUR5027 A , NUR0102 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.CODE_TYPE = 'NURSE_GRADE' AND A.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.NUR_GRADE(+) = B.CODE AND A.NUR_WRDT(+) = :f_date AND A.HO_DONG(+) = :f_ho_dong

data.name: fwkNurse.InputSQL
data.value: SELECT B.USER_ID , B.USER_NM FROM ADM3200 B WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND (B.USER_END_YMD IS NULL OR SYSDATE < B.USER_END_YMD) AND (B.USER_ID LIKE TRIM(:f_find1)||'%' OR B.USER_NM LIKE '%' || :f_find1 || '%') AND B.USER_GUBUN = '2' AND B.DEPT_CODE = :f_buseo_code ORDER BY 2

data.name: grdNurse.QuerySQL
data.value: /* SELECT NUR_WRDT , HO_DONG , NURSE_GRADE , WORK_TYPE , NURSE_ID , FN_ADM_LOAD_USER_NAME(NURSE_ID) , FN_NUR_LOAD_CODE_NAME('NURSE_GRADE', NURSE_GRADE) , FN_NUR_LOAD_CODE_NAME('WORK_TYPE_IN', WORK_TYPE) FROM NUR5022 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND NUR_WRDT = :f_date ORDER BY WORK_TYPE, NURSE_GRADE, NURSE_ID */

data.name: layTotalCnt.QuerySQL
data.value:
SELECT A.YESTERDAY_CNT --FN_INP_LOAD_JAEWON_CNT(:f_ho_dong, TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') - 1) YESTERDAY_CNT , B.IPWON_CNT , C.TOIWON_CNT , D.JAEWON_CNT , E.JUNCHUL , F.JUNIP --, FN_INP_LOAD_JAEWON_CNT(:f_ho_dong, TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD')) JAEWON_CNT FROM ( SELECT COUNT(BUNHO) YESTERDAY_CNT FROM INP1001 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong AND BUNHO NOT LIKE '5%' AND JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND IPWON_TYPE = '0' AND NVL(CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(TOIWON_CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND IPWON_DATE <= TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') - 1 AND NVL(TOIWON_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31','YYYY/MM/DD')) > TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') - 1 ) A, ( SELECT COUNT(BUNHO) IPWON_CNT FROM INP1001 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong AND BUNHO NOT LIKE '5%' --AND A.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND IPWON_TYPE = '0' AND NVL(CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(TOIWON_CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND IPWON_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) B, ( SELECT COUNT(BUNHO) TOIWON_CNT FROM INP1001 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong AND BUNHO NOT LIKE '5%' --AND A.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND IPWON_TYPE = '0' AND NVL(CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(TOIWON_CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND TOIWON_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') )C, ( SELECT COUNT(BUNHO) JAEWON_CNT FROM INP1001 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong AND BUNHO NOT LIKE '5%' AND JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND IPWON_TYPE = '0' AND NVL(CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(TOIWON_CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND IPWON_DATE <= TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND NVL(TOIWON_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31','YYYY/MM/DD')) > TO_DATE(:f_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') ) D, ( SELECT COUNT(*) JUNCHUL FROM INP2004 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.START_DATE = :f_date AND A.FROM_KAIKEI_HODONG != A.TO_KAIKEI_HODONG AND A.FROM_KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong ORDER BY A.SYS_DATE DESC) E,
( SELECT COUNT(*) JUNIP FROM INP2004 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.START_DATE = :f_date AND A.FROM_KAIKEI_HODONG != A.TO_KAIKEI_HODONG AND A.TO_KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong ORDER BY A.SYS_DATE DESC)F

data.name: layStairCnt.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT NVL(SUM(DECODE(Z.DIRECT_CONT1,'1',1,0)), 0) DANSONG, NVL(SUM(DECODE(Z.DIRECT_CONT1,'2',1,0)), 0) HOSONG, NVL(SUM(DECODE(NVL(Z.DIRECT_CONT1, '3'),'3',1,0)), 0) DOKBO, NVL(SUM(1), 0) TOT_CNT FROM ( SELECT A.FKINP1001 FKINP1001 , A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE , A.DIRECT_CONT1 DIRECT_CONT1 FROM OCS2005 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.DIRECT_CODE = '0021' AND A.ORDER_DATE = ( SELECT MAX(Z.ORDER_DATE) FROM OCS2005 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.FKINP1001 = A.FKINP1001 AND Z.DIRECT_GUBUN = A.DIRECT_GUBUN AND Z.DIRECT_CODE = A.DIRECT_CODE AND Z.ORDER_DATE <= :f_date )) Z , VW_OCS_INP1001_01 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong -- AND B.HO_CODE1 LIKE :f_stair||'%' AND B.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND B.BUNHO NOT LIKE '5%' AND NVL(B.CANCEL_YN,'N') = 'N' AND Z.FKINP1001(+) = B.PKINP1001

data.name: layGamyumCnt.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT SUM(COUNT(DECODE(A.INFE_CODE, '01', 1))) CNT1 --TPHA , SUM(COUNT(DECODE(A.INFE_CODE, '02', 1))) CNT2 --HBs , SUM(COUNT(DECODE(A.INFE_CODE, '03', 1))) CNT3 --HCV , SUM(COUNT(DECODE(A.INFE_CODE, '04', 1))) CNT4 --MRSA , SUM(COUNT(DECODE(A.INFE_CODE, '05', 1))) CNT5 --縁膿菌 FROM NUR1017 A , INP1001 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.KAIKEI_HODONG = :f_ho_dong AND NVL(B.CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(B.TOIWON_CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND NVL(A.CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND B.BUNHO NOT LIKE '5%' AND B.IPWON_TYPE IN ('0', '1') AND B.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND A.BUNHO = B.BUNHO AND :f_date BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND NVL(A.END_DATE, TO_DATE('9998/12/31', 'YYYY/MM/DD')) GROUP BY A.INFE_CODE

data.name: layConfirm_yn.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.CONFIRM_YN FROM NUR5200 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.NUR_WRDT = :f_date AND A.HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong --AND NVL(A.CONFIRM_YN, 'N') = 'Y' AND A.SEQ = (SELECT MAX(Z.SEQ) FROM NUR5200 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.NUR_WRDT = A.NUR_WRDT AND Z.HO_DONG = A.HO_DONG )

data.name: layPatientInfo_in.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HO_DONG1 HO_DONG , A.HO_CODE1 HO_CODE , B.SUNAME SUNAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(:f_nur_wrdt, B.BIRTH,'') AGE , B.SEX SEX , FN_OCS_LOAD_SANG_NAME(A.BUNHO, A.PKINP1001) SANG_NAME , A.GWA FROM INP1001 A , OUT0101 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO AND A.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND NVL(A.CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND A.IPWON_TYPE = '0'

data.name: layPatientInfo_out.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.HO_DONG1 HO_DONG , A.HO_CODE1 HO_CODE , B.SUNAME SUNAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_AGE(:f_nur_wrdt, B.BIRTH,'') AGE , B.SEX SEX , FN_OCS_LOAD_SANG_NAME(A.BUNHO, A.PKINP1001) SANG_NAME , A.GWA FROM INP1001 A , OUT0101 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND B.BUNHO = A.BUNHO --AND A.JAEWON_FLAG = 'Y' AND NVL(A.CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' AND A.IPWON_TYPE = '0' AND NVL(A.TOIWON_CANCEL_YN, 'N') = 'N' --AND A.TOIWON_DATE = :f_nur_wrdt AND A.PKINP1001 = (SELECT MAX(PKINP1001) FROM INP1001 X WHERE X.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND X.BUNHO = A.BUNHO)

data.name: layNur5020.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT YESTERDAY_CNT , IPWON_CNT , TOIWON_CNT , JAEWON_CNT , MOVE_OUT_CNT , MOVE_IN_CNT , GAMYUM1_CNT , GAMYUM2_CNT , GAMYUM3_CNT , GAMYUM4_CNT , GAMYUM5_CNT , GAMYUM6_CNT , GAMYUM7_CNT , GAMYUM8_CNT , GAMYUM6_NAME , GAMYUM7_NAME , GAMYUM8_NAME , YOKCHANG_NURSE , FN_ADM_LOAD_USER_NAME(YOKCHANG_NURSE) , YOKCHANG_COMMENT , NUR_WRDT , FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', NUR_WRDT) , HO_DONG , FN_BAS_LOAD_HO_DONG_NAME(HO_DONG, NUR_WRDT) FROM NUR5020 WHERE HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND HO_DONG = :f_ho_dong AND NUR_WRDT = :f_date

data.name: layNurCnt.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT FN_NUR_LOAD_CODE_NAME('NURSE_GRADE', B.CODE) NURSE_GRADE_NAME , COUNT(DECODE(A.WORK_TYPE, '01',1)) EARLY_CNT , COUNT(DECODE(A.WORK_TYPE, '02',1)) DAY_CNT , COUNT(DECODE(A.WORK_TYPE, '03',1)) LATE_CNT , COUNT(DECODE(A.WORK_TYPE, '04',1)) NIGHT_CNT , COUNT(DECODE(A.WORK_TYPE, '05',1)) HOLY_CNT , COUNT(DECODE(A.WORK_TYPE, '06',1)) VAC_CNT FROM NUR5022 A , NUR0102 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.NURSE_GRADE(+) = B.CODE AND B.CODE_TYPE = 'NURSE_GRADE' AND A.NUR_WRDT(+) = :f_nur_wrdt GROUP BY B.CODE ORDER BY B.CODE
